## Next Milestones

1. Monitor post-release feedback and issues.
2. Plan the next feature iteration.
3. Subscription system block (email double opt-in + Sileo notifications) implemented in `apps/web` on 2026-05-20, including standalone subscription banner (moved out of footer) and unsubscribe flow.
4. Add minimal admin operations surface for subscriptions (list/status change/delete/trigger notify) with secure access strategy.
5. Roll out production env + SMTP and run end-to-end verification on deployed domain.
6. Subscription banner form card: added cmd+kit brand logo in form header (theme-aware light/dark asset) on 2026-05-20.
7. Admin hardening (2026-05-20): add `/admin` gate page, server-side block on `/admin/subscriptions`, and HttpOnly cookie session after magic link.
8. Magic link delivery hardening (2026-05-20): support `SUPABASE_KEY` env alias, keep canonical redirect on `APP_BASE_URL`, and allow first-login OTP user creation for allowlisted admin emails.
9. Admin notify UX (2026-05-20): centered custom modal, resource catalog search/add flow, multi-resource digest send, and iconized admin actions.
10. Admin operational diagnostics (2026-05-20): add protected health endpoint for subscription stack config checks and in-panel health card.
11. Admin SMTP E2E verification (2026-05-21): add protected `Send test email` action to validate real delivery from admin panel.
12. NPM release notify flow (2026-05-21): switch admin notify catalog to tracked npm packages, fetch live versions from npm registry with cache, and support one/some/all selection semantics.
13. Notification email quality (2026-05-21): generic copy by scope (single/some/all), favicon header image, and direct Gravatar avatar URL for stable rendering.
14. Icon cleanup (2026-05-21): remove spark/sparkles usage across web surfaces and replace with contextual icons (search/code/menu).
11. Admin SMTP E2E verification (2026-05-21): add protected `Send test email` action to validate real delivery from production/admin panel.
15. Docs npm linking (2026-05-21): add direct npm package links in docs getting-started and each package page (EN/ES).
16. Cross-package hover consistency (2026-05-21): unify close `X` hover/border/background tokens with theme accent hover colors in core, Vue, and Preact so custom hover palette is always respected.
17. Global palette scaling API (2026-05-21): add `size` prop (`small | normal | large`) across core/react/preact/vue/astro so command palette scales uniformly with preserved visual proportions.
18. Docs subnav polish (2026-05-21): replace per-item markers with one animated rail dot that moves to active section.
